OL,5, David Cameron's government knew the    
OL,6, Post Office had ditched a secret       
OL,7, investigation that might have helped   
OL,8, wrongly accused postmasters prove their
OL,9, innocence, the BBC can reveal.         
OL,11,FThe 2016 investigation trawled 17 years
OL,12,Fof records to find out how often, and  
OL,13,Fwhy, cash accounts on the Horizon IT   
OL,14,Fsystem had been tampered with remotely.
OL,16,FMinisters were told an investigation   
OL,17,Fwas happening.                         
OL,19,FBut after postmasters began legal      
OL,20,Faction, it was suddenly stopped.       
